							singleType="STRING";
							value="Your main objective for this mission is to find and extract a high-ranking rebel warlord. Find him and capture him, we need to debrief him on the ship, once captured take him to the exfil area. He may be armed so approach with caution, use flashbangs, wound him or attempt to incapacitate him.<br/><br/>Once you reach the HVT the entire island will respond, take note of the QRF Stations and attempt to avoid the incoming trackers. They will hunt you, so be prepared to move fast!<br/><br/>If for any reason you are unable to reach your own boat, you can commandeer civilian boats along the north-east coastline.";
